Sanitarium So Good Barista Soy Milk is a long life dairy free milk made for coffee
It can be hard to replicate the cafe coffee experience at home. So Good has worked with Australian barista and cafe owners to develop the ideal soy milk for coffee, allowing you to make cafe quality coffee in the comfort of your own kitchen.

So Good™ Barista soy is low in saturated fat, sugars and sodium. With protein and essential minerals, it’s also naturally lactose and cholesterol free. These are important factors which contribute to the 5 star rating that So Good Barista soy achieves.

Head to the dairy free aisle to pick up your So Good on your next shop.
